reviewText: Movie is great, action drama. must see
Short duration  video of a long timespan. Seems jumpy and disjointed. Characters don't have a lot of time to develop. Interesting story.
Fernando Solorzano VERY GOOD ACTOR, Marlon Moreno excellent too!  Christina Umana good actress, broad range.  Highly recomment it. Take awhile to follow the sequence of events. But good.
